(26, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Parle Products enters cereal category with Hide & Seek Fills</h1>', 'fills.jpg', 'fills.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif;\">Parle\r\nProducts, India\'s leading biscuits, snacks and confectionery manufacturer,\r\nannounced its entry into the cereals category with the launch of \'Hide &\r\nSeek Fills\'. The company aims to produce highly nutritious cereals for an\r\nenergizing breakfast and strengthen its product portfolio for consumers in all\r\nage groups. To build on the legacy of quality and experience, the company\'s\r\npremium \'Platina\' range</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">Parle\'s \'Hide & Seek Fills\' is the first step forward in building the broader cereal category</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Parle Products, India\'s leading biscuits, snacks and confectionery manufacturer,\r\nannounced its entry into the cereals category with the launch of \'Hide &\r\nSeek Fills\'. The company aims to produce highly nutritious cereals for an\r\nenergizing breakfast and strengthen its product portfolio for consumers in all\r\nage groups. To build on the legacy of quality and experience, the company\'s\r\npremium \'Platina\' range will bring an exciting mix of healthy and indulgent\r\nofferings into the newly launched segment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">According\r\nto the company, Hide & Seek Fills will continue the renowned rich chocolaty\r\nexperience established by Hide & Seek, the iconic Chocolate Chip Cookies,\r\nwhich debuted in 1996. The new product will take advantage of the kids snacking\r\nmarket opportunities by providing 50% premium chocolate filling to satisfy\r\nhunger pangs, serve as a quick breakfast, and offer a quick sumptuous snack.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">With\r\nthe new category introduction, Parle Products will bring innovation to the line\r\nof breakfast cereals while providing affordable products to customers without\r\ncompromising on health or taste. Hide & Seek Fills, offered at Rs 10 packs\r\nacross India, is the first step in expanding the cereal category.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Speaking\r\non the launch, Krishnarao Buddha, senior category head, Parle Products, said,\r\n\"Our deep knowledge of consumer behavior and patterns has enabled us to\r\nmeet the consumers where they are today. Our understanding indicated that many\r\npeople prefer breakfast cereals as healthy options for themselves and their\r\nkids. By extending Parle\'s portfolio, our goal is to provide consumers with\r\nquick and healthy breakfast choices. Our entry into the niche breakfast cereal\r\nindustry will give a fresh perception of the values and character represented\r\nby the \'Parle Products\' name.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">\"The\r\nnew product - Hide & Seek Fills\' crispy and melt-in-your-mouth experience\r\nwill incite a luxurious experience and we are confident that consumers will\r\nlove to have \'Hide & Seek Fills\' as their preferred breakfast option. As a\r\npurposive approach with this launch, we intend to expand our reach and showcase\r\ncontinued commitment towards our customers.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Within\r\nthe consumer products market, Parle Products has one of the highest reaches in\r\nterms of distribution at about 8 million outlets. In June this year, the\r\ncompany also entered the Aata segment.</p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#parle #Cereal #Krishnarao #nutrition #productlaunch', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-09-28 03:47:26', '2021-10-08 01:28:15', 'admin', 0),
