ering products like quick-to-cook Chinese masalas, uniquely\r\nflavored noodles, sumptuous soups, and a first-of-its-kind â€“ the versatile\r\nSchezwan Chutney. Smith & Jones specializes in condiments and cooking\r\npastes, fusing local and international flavors.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#capitalfoods #wholewheat #noodles #productlaunch', 'Yes', NULL, '388', NULL, NULL, '2021-09-28 04:02:42', '2021-09-28 05:51:50', 'admin', 0);
