(28, 'Bhavna Suresh Co-founder and CEO of the startup 10Club, secured $40 million in seed funding', 'ladki.jpg', 'ladki.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-family: museo-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 17.92px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;\">Women-led startups raising venture capital funding, even today, is rare. And, if one of them ends up grabbing one of the largest seed rounds, it is definitely a point of discussion.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-family: museo-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 17.92px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;\">And, Bhavna Suresh grabbed the eyeballs of the Indian startup ecosystem when</span></p><p><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">Women-led startups raising venture capital funding, even today, is rare. And, if one of them ends up grabbing one of the largest seed rounds, it is definitely a point of discussion.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" >And, Bhavna Suresh grabbed the eyeballs of the Indian startup ecosystem when her D2C startupÂ <span class=\"company-widget embed\" id=\"e3c1fa50-0edb-11ec-929e-a38faec9a5ca\" data-name=\"10Club\" data-id=\"e3c1fa50-0edb-11ec-929e-a38faec9a5ca\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-vars-company-name=\"10Club\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: none; display: inline-block; font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18px;\">ï»¿<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">10Club</span>ï»¿</span>Â secured $40 million in seed funding.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The Thrasio-like startupâ€”Â <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 800;\">founded by Bhavna, Deepak Nair, and Joel Ayala</span>Â â€” focuses on small businesses and startups, where it acquires them, keeps the team and the founders onboard, gives them the agreed-upon stakes, and helps them scale the business.Â </p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: museo-sans, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-size: 1.12rem; line-height: 2rem; letter-spacing: 0.18px;\">But this isnâ€™t Bhavnaâ€™s first rodeo. Besides her previous startup, Stylebank, Bhavna was also the CEO of Lamudi Paris.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">â€œWhile I did do the usual route of engineering from the Vishveshvarya Institute of Technology, and later an MBA from HEC Paris, I have always done something different and away from the norm. Even in my mechanical engineering course, I was one of the few women in my class,â€ shares Bhavna.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<h5  class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Not without challenges</h5>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">In fact, Bhavna was the first female mechanical engineer at a large automobile company. She says while being the first is great, it can be challenging too.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">\r\n<blockquote class=\"font-experiment-bq\">â€œThese are people who have been comfortable in their biases and expect women to behave in a certain way. And, here I was doing things on the field, getting down and dirty. While it took some initial challenges to overcome, soon things changed, and I got the support that I needed,â€ Bhavna says.Â </blockquote>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">By the age of 25, Bhavna built a whole sales division from scratch and launched operations successfully in 10 months. For this, she was recognised as the manager with the fastest turnaround time to set up a fully operational market by a company.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">She also worked for digital agency 22Feet for two years, post which she decided to get into fashion during her MBA days, and Stylebank was born in 2016.Â </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Bhavna had met with a few investors and a partner in India and had begun building the company. Stylebank was an online fashion rental service space. While it was working well as a niche, the timing of starting up in the space wasnâ€™t right, and the journey was short-lived.Â </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">After a break, she was called by Lamudi, a real estate listings site backed by Rocket Internet, to head the company operations and grow the business. â€œIt was something I simply couldnâ€™t say no to,â€ adds Bhavna.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Prop-tech startup Lamudi had started operations in 2014. She helped the company grow till it got acquired by EMPG in February 2020.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Bhavna reconnected with Deepak from 22Feet, also a startup mentor, and decided to start 10Club. â€œIt took us till January 2021 to research, and we spoke with over 300 sellers to understand the need of the market and the categories we could operate in,â€ says Bhavna.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recently, the D2C startup raised $40 million in seed funding led by Fireside Ventures and has acquired a baby startup, My NewBorn.Â </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Advising young women, who want to get on their entrepreneurship journey, Bhavna says, â€œDo your research and work hard on what you need to do. Stop at nothing to achieve what you want. And build your network.â€Â </p>', 'Wonder-Woman', '', '#wonderwoman', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-09-28 06:58:14', '2021-10-08 03:09:35', 'admin', 0),
(29, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Duroflex launches â€˜Change your sleep, change your\r\nlifeâ€™ campaign with brand ambassador Alia Bhatt</h1>', 'aaliya.jpg', 'aaliya.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4pt;\">Sleep solutions brand Duroflex is spreading\r\nthe festive cheer with a campaign for Diwali featuring national brand\r\nambassador Alia Bhatt, putting the spotlight on <b>â€˜Change your sleep, change\r\nyour life.â€™<o:p></o:p></b></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0.4pt;\">Over\r\nthe years, doing home renovations, upgrading durables and buying automobiles\r\nhave become the norm during Diwali. This year, Duroflex and Bhatt are urging\r\nIndians to celebrate Diwali by making a meaningful</span></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">The brand has launched the campaign conceived by Creativeland Asia nationally\r\nthrough a multi-channel strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Sleep solutions brand Duroflex is spreading\r\nthe festive cheer with a campaign for Diwali featuring national brand\r\nambassador Alia Bhatt, putting the spotlight on <b>â€˜Change your sleep, change\r\nyour life.</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Over the years, doing home renovations,\r\nupgrading durables and buying automobiles have become the norm during Diwali.\r\nThis year, Duroflex and Bhatt are urging Indians to celebrate Diwali by making\r\na meaningful lifestyle changeâ€” upgrading sleep essentials that can enable deep\r\nhealthy sleep for a better life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">This important message is brought alive in the\r\nbrandâ€™s Diwali communication, where Alia Bhatt will be seen with her real-life\r\nbest friend, Akansha Ranjan Kapoor, for the very first time on screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">In the film, Bhatt endearingly nudges Kapoor,\r\nwho is considering a big change this Diwali to change her old mattress and\r\ninvest in a doctor-recommended Duroflex mattress.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Bhatt emphasises on what differentiates\r\nresearch-backed Duroflex mattresses from the rest. Duroflexâ€™s signature range\r\nof mattresses come with 50 years of trust, five-zoned full-body support, and is\r\ndoctor recommended by the National Health Academy. The film ends with Kapoor\r\nsleeping peacefully on a Duroflex mattress and Bhatt bringing alive the message\r\nof â€˜Nothing Like Duroflex.â€™\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Smita Murarka, Chief Marketing Officer,\r\nDuroflex, said, â€œFestivals in India are auspicious occasions for embracing\r\nchanges that add value to oneâ€™s life. Over the years, upgrading home durables,\r\ndÃ©cor and lifestyle products have become customary to Diwali shopping. This\r\nyear, we are inspiring to people to make the biggest change of all through our\r\nmessage â€˜Change your sleep, change your Lifeâ€™. Our campaign shows Alia Bhatt\r\nenlightening her best friend Akansha, who is seeking a big change, to upgrade\r\nher mattress and bring home a doctor-recommended mattress by Duroflex. As a\r\nsleep solution brand with over five decades of expertise, we strongly believe\r\nthat good sleep on a research-backed mattress can deeply enrich oneâ€™s life. We\r\nhave been leading this change with our innovative sleep product and\r\ncommunication over the years.â€</p>', 'Marketing-Campaign', '', '#Duroflex#aaliyabhat', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-09-28 22:29:16', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(30, '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif\">Dabur forays\r\ninto new category, launches Dabur Vatika Face Wash range<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', 'vatika.jpg', 'vatika.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Dabur Vatika,&nbsp;a\r\npersonal care brand from the house of Dabur</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">, has announced its\r\nforay into the face wash category with the launch of Dabur Vatika Face Wash\r\nrange. Strengthening Daburâ€™s presence in the personal care market in India,\r\nthis range has been launched with e-commerce platform Flipkart.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Priced at MRP Rs\r\n170,&nbsp;the New Vatika Face Wash&nbsp;will be&nbsp;available in a 150ml\r\nSKU.&nbsp;It&nbsp;comes in three variants â€“ Vatika Neem Purifying&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif\">The new Vatika range comes in\r\nthree variants â€”Vatika Neem Purifying Face Wash, Vatika Sandalwood Illuminating\r\nFace Wash and Vatika Honey Moisture Boost Face Wash<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Dabur Vatika,&nbsp;a\r\npersonal care brand from the house of Dabur</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">, has announced its\r\nforay into the face wash category with the launch of Dabur Vatika Face Wash\r\nrange. Strengthening Daburâ€™s presence in the personal care market in India,\r\nthis range has been launched with e-commerce platform Flipkart.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Priced at MRP Rs\r\n170,&nbsp;the New Vatika Face Wash&nbsp;will be&nbsp;available in a 150ml\r\nSKU.&nbsp;It&nbsp;comes in three variants â€“ Vatika Neem Purifying Face Wash,\r\nVatika Sandalwood Illuminating Face Wash and Vatika Honey Moisture Boost Face\r\nWash.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Rajat Mathur, AGM,\r\nConsumer MarketingÂ­Â­Â­Â­Â­Â­Â­Â­, Dabur India Ltd, said, \"Vatika has always\r\nrecognised and strived to meet the ever-evolving needs of our consumers. We are\r\nexcited to strengthen our Vatika portfolio with the launch of new Vatika Face\r\nWash. Be it Hair Oil or Shampoo, Dabur Vatika has evolved as the preferred\r\npersonal care brand for millions of consumers over the years.&nbsp;With the\r\nNew&nbsp;Vatika Face Wash, we are expanding the Vatika franchise to give consumers\r\na soap and paraben-free product for their daily face care needs.â€<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">K. Ganapathy\r\nSubramaniam, DGM, Marketing (Innovations), Dabur India Ltd, said,\r\nâ€œThe&nbsp;launch of Vatika Face Wash demonstrates Dabur\'s continued commitment\r\nto providing innovative natural skin care products of the highest quality\r\nstandards, without compromise.&nbsp;Each variant of the new range has a unique\r\ningredient that solves specific face-skin problems. Vatika Face Wash is\r\ndermatologically tested and is paraben and soap-free and has 100% natural\r\nactives.&nbsp;We continue to research and co-create products with Flipkart to\r\noffer our consumers a world-class personal care product range.â€<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Manish Kumar, Senior\r\nVice-President, Beauty, General Merchandise and Home,&nbsp;Flipkart, said, â€œAs\r\na homegrown company, Flipkart is deeply committed to bringing the most relevant\r\nproducts to its consumers, through its marketplace. With the changing external\r\nenvironment, we have witnessed consumers becoming more aware of the\r\nenvironmental impact and benefits of using organic/natural products. Keeping up\r\nwith these insights, we are excited to co-create and bring Daburâ€™s new Vatika\r\nFace Wash to the market. As a strategic partner of the brand, we share a common\r\ncause â€“ bringing high-quality products to Indian consumers that cater to their\r\nneeds.\"<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">â€œDabur has always bet\r\nbig on e-commerce as a channel of the future. Our continuous effort has been to\r\ngive our shoppers something new and exciting. The Vatika Face Wash range is our\r\nlatest offering in this endeavour. It was a sheer delight to co-create this\r\nproduct along with Flipkart, one of our strategic partners. Both Dabur and\r\nFlipkart teams have worked closely to understand the emerging trends in the\r\nnatural ingredient-based face wash category to come up with this natural range.\r\nI believe the new Vatika Face Wash will be immensely loved by our\r\nshoppers,â€&nbsp;said Smerth Khanna, Business Head E-commerce, Dabur India Ltd.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Vatika Neem Purifying\r\nFace Wash is packed with the goodness of neem extracts and Vitamin E. It helps\r\ncontrol pimples, removes excess oil from the skin, fights skin breakouts and\r\npurifies face leaving it fresh, healthy and glowing. Vatika Sandalwood\r\nIlluminating Face Wash has key ingredients such as sandalwood oil and saffron.\r\nIt illuminates your face, helps in reducing pigmentation, cleans, refreshes and\r\nrevitalises your face making it look healthy.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Vatika Honey Moisture\r\nBoost Face Wash has the goodness of honey, which boosts face moisture, almond\r\nwhich protects moisture-barrier and aloe vera, which helps retain moisture and\r\nsoothes the face. It cleanses the face, keeps the skin supple, moisturises and\r\nsoothes the face.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#vatika #dabur #facewash #productlaunch', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-09-28 22:31:09', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(31, '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:\r\n\" trebuchet=\"\" ms\",sans-serif\"=\"\">OPPO India welcomes the Festive Season with\r\nspecial-edition launches of OPPO Reno6 Pro 5G Diwali edition, OPPO F19s and\r\nOPPO Enco Buds Blue<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', 'oppo.jpg', 'oppo.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">OPPO, today announced the\r\nlaunch of its Special Editions this festive season. The product line-up\r\nincludes the all-new OPPO Reno6 Pro 5G Gold Diwali edition which is priced at\r\nINR 41,990 the F19s, priced at INR 19,990 and the Enco Buds in a new blue color\r\nvariant, priced at INR 1,999.Â Â Customers can get their hands on the\r\nOPPO F19s from 27thÂ September at 4PM, OPPO Reno6 Pro 5G Diwali Edition and\r\nOPPO Enco Buds Blue from 3rdÂ October 2021, on Flipkart and mainlineÂ </span><br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">OPPO, today\r\nannounced the launch of its Special Editions this festive season. The product\r\nline-up includes the all-new OPPO Reno6 Pro 5G Gold Diwali edition which is\r\npriced at INR 41,990 the F19s, priced at INR 19,990 and the Enco Buds in a new\r\nblue color variant, priced at INR 1,999.Â Â Customers can get their\r\nhands on the OPPO F19s from 27thÂ September at 4PM, OPPO Reno6 Pro 5G\r\nDiwali Edition and OPPO Enco Buds Blue from 3rdÂ October 2021, on Flipkart\r\nand mainline retailers.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\