G Diwali edition</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">Â comes\r\nin a Majestic Gold color with a matching wallpaper, UI and charging interface.\r\nThe OPPO Reno6 Pro 5G features industry-first Bokeh Flare Portrait Video that\r\nprovides cinematic bokeh flare effects in portraits and AI Highlight Video,\r\nenables you to capture professional-grade videos in real time. The Reno6 Pro 5G\r\nalso features the latest flagship MediaTek Dimensity 1200 chipset, OPPO\'s\r\nexclusive Reno Glow design, Smart 5G capabilities, ColorOS 11.3, 4500 mAh\r\nbattery and 65W SuperVOOC 2.0 fast charging capabilities. All this within a\r\nsleek, light-weight body.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">Â <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">Along with the OPPO\r\nReno6 Pro 5G Diwali edition, OPPO has also launched the newÂ </span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nHelvetica;color:#333333\">Special Edition OPPO F19s</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">Â in\r\nIndia. The device is the sleekest smartphone with a 5000mAh battery, an comes\r\nwith an AMOLED display and OPPOâ€™s proprietary 33W flash-charging technology\r\nthat promises a higher level of safety with its night-charging protection and\r\ntemperature control. The smartphone can be fully charged in 72 minutes, and you\r\ncan expect 5 hours 45 minutes of calling or around 2 hours of YouTube with just\r\na 5-minute recharge. In keeping with the festive theme, this new Special\r\nEdition OPPO F19s boasts India\'s First AG design that gives the smartphone its\r\nspecial gold color. The F19s is an addition to the current F-series line-up\r\nthat includes the F19, F19 Pro, and F19 Pro+ 5G and the smartphone will be\r\navailable in Glowing Black and Glowing Golden.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">In\r\naddition to these, OPPO also announced the launch of its entry-levelÂ </span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Enco Buds Blue</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">. The new TWS delivers concert-like audio, packs AI-based\r\ncall noise-cancellation technology and comes with a 24-hour battery life. The\r\noffering is specifically built for users who want to upgrade from their wired-\r\nand traditional Bluetooth earphones to their first truly wireless earbuds.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">Speaking about the\r\ncampaign and the upcoming launches,Â </span></i><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Damyant Singh Khanoria, Chief Marketing Officer â€“ OPPO India</span></strong><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">, said â€œ</span></i><em><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nHelvetica;color:#333333\">OPPO believes in building technology for mankind and\r\nour products are a true testament to this very commitment.Â Â We are\r\nthrilled to announce the launch of our special editions line up to spread the\r\npositivity and festive cheer. Whether you are a new age video creator who wants\r\na videography superphone or just someone who wants to flaunt a sleek and\r\nstylish smartphone, we have something for everybody.</span></em><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"Trebuchet MS\",sans-serif;color:#333333\">â€<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#oppo#F19s#5G', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-09-28 22:34:09', '2021-09-28 23:15:30', 'admin', 0),
(32, '<h1  id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Madhav Sheth promoted as VP, realme, and CEO, realme\r\nIndia, Europe and Latin America</h1>', 'inside.jpg', 'inside.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif\">Madhav Sheth, Vice-President of\r\nrealme and CEO, realme India and Europe, has been elevated to spearhead\r\nrealmeâ€™s presence and business operations in the Latin<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.4pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">-</span></strong>America\r\nregion.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Under the new designation\r\nof Vice-President, realme, and CEO, realme India, Europe and Latin America,\r\nSheth will lead product, marketing, brand-building and sales functions in these\r\nregions. The foray into a new and promising&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">In\r\nhis new role, Madhav Sheth will be looking at growing realmeâ€™s brand presence\r\nand business operations in the Latin-American region<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Madhav Sheth, Vice-President of\r\nrealme and CEO, realme India and Europe, has been elevated to spearhead\r\nrealmeâ€™s presence and business operations in the Latin<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.4pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">-</span></strong>America\r\nregion.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p  class=\"text-justify\">Under the new designation of\r\nVice-President, realme, and CEO, realme India, Europe and Latin America, Sheth\r\nwill lead product, marketing, brand-building and sales functions in these\r\nregions. The foray into a new and promising market reflects realmeâ€™s vision to\r\nbring trendsetting technology and leapfrogging performance to the consumers in\r\nthe region, enabling it to achieve its ambition of gaining dual 100 million\r\nusers by 2023 and build its way to a leading tech brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">In Mexico and Brazil, realme will\r\nprioritize product development, which is always a top priority for the company\r\nand will aim towards building a strong local workforce in the Latin American\r\nregion. Latin America is a promising market for feature-rich, performance-savvy\r\nsmartphones and realme aims to fill in the gap in the needs of young audiences\r\nand continue to launch products with cutting-edge performance and trendsetting\r\ndesign at democratized pricing, which have played as a key growth driver. In\r\naddition, realme will optimize its market and channel strategies in Mexico and\r\nBrazil. Under Shethâ€™s stewardship, realme has ascended to the top five vendors\r\nin Europe in Q2 2021 as per Strategy Analytics, and the company plans to do the\r\nsame in Mexico and Brazil next year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Realme has announced its realme\r\nTechLife Ecosystem with a vision of â€˜Technology that Empowers Lifeâ€™ and a\r\nmission to create a smart, connected and trendy lifestyle for the youth,\r\nsupported by its 1+5+T strategy. realme will gradually introduce realme\r\nTechLife Ecosystem In Latin America also.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Realme is a technology brand that\r\nspecializes in providing high-quality smartphones and a trendsetting tech\r\nlifestyle. The brand was officially established on May 4, 2018 by its founder\r\nSky Li and Madhav Sheth in India, together with a young team.</p>', 'Inside-Edge', '', '#Madhav#realme#ceo', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-01 00:32:48', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(33, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Society\r\nTea introduces instant dairy whitener \'Society Dairy White\'</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', 'society.jpg', 'society.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Mumbai-based\r\nSociety Tea, an Indian tea brand, has recently added Society Dairy White to its\r\nproduct portfolio. According to the company, the Society Dairy White is best\r\nfor making tea, coffee, milk beverages, breakfast cereals, milk desserts and&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Mumbai-based Society Tea, an Indian tea brand, has recently added\r\nSociety Dairy White to its product portfolio. According to the company, the\r\nSociety Dairy White is best for making tea, coffee, milk beverages, breakfast\r\ncereals, milk desserts and sweets.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Society Dairy White is available in 200 grams pack at Rs 90.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Society Tea today is the market leader in the Tea category in\r\nMumbai and has become a dominant force. The brand has a considerable presence\r\nin other states such as Goa, Andhra Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Karnataka,\r\nChennai, Punjab, Rajasthan and Delhi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 11.25pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Since its inception, Society Tea has always aimed to keep quality\r\nat the highest possible levels for all its products. To ensure this consistent\r\nquality, three family members have dedicated their lives as full-time tea\r\ntasters.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 11.25pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">To manufacture high-quality Tea and Dairy products, Society Tea\r\nhas set up a plant in Vadodara (Gujarat). This plant is one of India\'s most\r\nadvanced and completely automated milk and soluble tea processing units. It\r\nmanufactures these products under strict hygienic standards to meet its high\r\nlevels of quality and excellence.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#tea#dairy', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-01 00:34:57', NULL, '', 0),
