ornflakes offers something for everyone without\r\ncompromising on nutrition.â€<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#cornflakes#nourish', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-01 00:36:41', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(35, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Noise\r\nonboards Taapsee Pannu as brand ambassador</h1>', 'noise.jpg', 'noise.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Lifestyle brand NOISE has brought on board\r\nBollywood star Taapsee Pannu as brand ambassador for the smart wearable\r\ncategory. The actor will be a part of the upcoming brand campaigns wherein she\r\nwill promote its smartwatches including the next brand&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">The actor will be a part of\r\nupcoming brand campaigns promoting its smart wearables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Lifestyle\r\nbrand NOISE has brought on board Bollywood star Taapsee Pannu as brand\r\nambassador for the smart wearable category. The actor will be a part of the\r\nupcoming brand campaigns wherein she will promote its smartwatches including\r\nthe next brand offering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" >With\r\nthis announcement, Noise said it aims to reinforce its positioning as the\r\nleading homegrown smartwatch brand and liaison a deeper connect with fitness\r\nenthusiasts and millennials. â€œTaapseeâ€™s persona blends with Noiseâ€™s core belief\r\nin listening to the noise within and belief in oneselfâ€</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">â€œOur\r\nproducts are carefully designed keeping in mind the requirements of fitness and\r\nlifestyle enthusiasts who listen to their â€˜Dil ka Shorâ€™ and dare to carve a new\r\npathâ€, said Noise co-founder Gaurav Khatri. â€œNoiseâ€™s smartwatches and Taapsee,\r\nboth motivate individuals to take up new challenges every day. With her strong\r\npersona and our commitment to offering unparalleled experience, we want to\r\nstrengthen the trust of Noisemakersâ€.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">â€œI\r\nconstantly strive to accomplish new fitness goals every day to be ahead in the\r\ngame, likewise Noise. I have witnessed that more than ever, people are now\r\nconscious of the thriving fitness significance. Noiseâ€™s smartwatches act as the\r\nhealth pattern that consistently helps me to connect with my true selfâ€ said\r\nPannu on the association.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Noise\r\nis set to roll out new brand campaigns and launches in the next few months.</p>', 'Marketing-Campaign', '', '#taapseepannu#noise', 'Yes', NULL, '389', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-01 00:38:37', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(36, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Diljit Dosanjh is the new face for Fila in India</h1>', 'diljit.jpg', 'diljit.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.4pt;\">Diljit Dosanjh is the\r\nnew face of sport, leisure footwear and apparel brand Fila in India. There is a\r\ntrue vibe in this association, as both Dosanjh and Fila embody youthful energy,\r\nplayfulness and a distinct style</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">In\r\nthe campaign, Dosanjh will be seen sporting Filaâ€™s uber cool Motorsport\r\ncollection. This year, the collection debuts a line of apparel and footwear\r\ninfused with style and performance with a Motorsport edge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Diljit Dosanjh is the new face of sport,\r\nleisure footwear and apparel brand Fila in India. There is a true vibe in this\r\nassociation, as both Dosanjh and Fila embody youthful energy, playfulness and a\r\ndistinct style quotient.</p>  \r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">\r\nDosanjhâ€™s bold fashion statements are not only\r\ninspiring a whole new generation but his true love towards streetwear culture\r\nis also defining trends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">In the campaign, Dosanjh will be seen sporting\r\nFilaâ€™s uber cool Motorsport collection. Motorsport has always been a part of\r\nFilaâ€™s DNA and an essential category for the brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\"><span>This year, the collection debuts a line of\r\napparel and footwear infused with style and performance with a Motorsport edge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Dosanjh in his own style announced to the\r\nworld â€œHum Fila wale ban gayeâ€ (I have now become part of the Fila family),\r\nthrough his Instagram stories.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Rohan Batra, Managing Director, Cravatex\r\nBrands Limited, which has an exclusive license for the Brand Fila in India,\r\nsaid, â€œWe are extremely delighted to have Diljit Dosanjh as the face of the\r\nbrand in India. Diljit has effortlessly blended streetwear and culture and\r\ncontinues to be a massive influence on the youth of India. His approach matches\r\nthe philosophy of Fila, which caters to the everyday lifestyle of young\r\nconsumers, who are ambitious while being effortlessly fashionable. We could not\r\nhave asked for a better association than Diljit, whose style statement is\r\nauthentic and true.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The newly launched Motorsport collection is\r\navailable at Fila exclusive stores, leading large format stores and e-com\r\npartners. The range starts at Rs 3,000 and is designed for consumers who look\r\nat motorsport as fashion and lifestyle choice and not just a sport.</p>', 'Marketing-Campaign', '', '#Diljit#DiljitDosanjh#fila', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-06 02:27:57', NULL, 'admin', 0);
