(37, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Parle Agroâ€™s B-Fizz\r\nlaunches a high-decibel campaign with brand ambassador Arjun Kapoor</h1>', 'fizz.jpg', 'fizz.jpg', '<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">â€˜Be Bold, Be Braveâ€™</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\"> is the motto of\r\nParle Agroâ€™s malt flavoured fruit drink, B Fizz. The company has launched an\r\nedgy TV campaign for B Fizz with a rugged new face for the brand,</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Arjun Kapoor.\r\nUnveiling the new ambassador-drink duo through the ad, Parle Agro evokes a\r\nsense of fearlessness and boldness</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">Walsh, the creative agency\r\nfor B Fizz, has led the campaign narrative for the television commercials,\r\nprint and digital. The films have been produced by Ransom Films, and directed\r\nby John Poliquin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">\'Be Bold,\r\nBe Brave\' is the motto of Parle Agroâ€™s malt flavoured fruit drink, B Fizz.\r\nThe company has launched an edgy TV campaign for B Fizz with a rugged new face\r\nfor the brand, Arjun Kapoor. Unveiling the new ambassador-drink duo through the\r\nad, Parle Agro evokes a sense of fearlessness and boldness with B Fizz. Centred\r\non the taste profile, and vigorous spirit surrounding the imagery, the campaign\r\nfor B Fizz stands apart from any other drink in the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Parle Agro\r\nis looking to build tremendous buzz for B Fizz through a high-decibel marketing\r\ncampaign. The media campaign has been rolled out nationally across multiple\r\nchannels, including TV, OOH and Digital.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">B Fizz is\r\ncharacterized as a dynamic drink for the bold, and for those who look for newer\r\nexperiences and challenges which is underlined by new brand ambassador Kapoor\r\nin the TVC. The unmistakable red and white packaging coupled with its unique\r\ntaste appeals to consumers of all age groups and can be consumed at any time of\r\nthe day. Whether it is Diwali, New Yearâ€™s, or a house party, B Fizz is the\r\nparty-starter that will make you feel fearless but also wonâ€™t blur out memories\r\nyou most cherish. The malt flavoured fruit drink offers a unique taste and fizz\r\nthat is perfect for consumers who prefer non-alcoholic beverages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Nadia\r\nChauhan of Parle Agro</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> said, â€œParle Agro takes pride in being a pioneering beverage\r\nbrand that is not afraid to take risks to meet and exceed expectations of our\r\ncustomers. With B Fizz, we wanted to tap the audience that is bold, loves to\r\ntake risks and seeks new experiences. In our latest ad for B Fizz, we have\r\ncaptured this very sentiment through the imagery which is bold and edgy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Chauhan\r\nsaid, â€œArjun Kapoor is the perfect choice to represent the â€˜boldâ€™, â€˜uniqueâ€™\r\ncharacteristics of B Fizz and we are elated to have him on board as the\r\nambassador for the brand. Just like Arjunâ€™s personality, B Fizz too holds a\r\nstrong distinct character that cannot be compared to another. The refreshing\r\nduo is sure to drive reach and build greater visibility for the brand and make\r\nB Fizz an easy pick for beverage consumers across India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Brand\r\nambassador Kapoor said, â€œIâ€™m\r\nthrilled to be representing a unique, bold and revolutionary drink like B Fizz.\r\nThere are times when a brandâ€™s ideologies and your own personality harmonise\r\nperfectly, and my association with B Fizz is simply that. Shooting for the ad\r\nwas a great experience, especially because the brandâ€™s approach to advertising\r\nis so unique. Iâ€™m excited to be a part of Parle Agroâ€™s vision for the brand and\r\nlook forward to being part of their growth journey.â€</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Walsh,\r\nthe creative agency for B Fizz, has led the campaign narrative for the\r\ntelevision commercials, print and digital. The films have been produced by\r\nRansom Films, and directed by John Poliquin.</p>', 'Marketing-Campaign', '', '#fizz#arjunkapoor', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-06 02:30:04', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(38, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">On\r\nWorld Heart Day, Dhara puts spotlight on importance of heart health among young\r\nIndians</h1>', 'Dhara (2).png', 'Dhara (2).png', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Dhara, an edible oil brand from Mother Dairy,\r\nhas rolled out a digital film on the occasion of World Heart Day 2021,\r\nadvocating the importance of heart health, especially among young Indians under</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">The film subtly points\r\nout the urgent need for physical exercise, reduced stress and enhancing the\r\nintake of oryzanol in daily diet as key to heart health.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">\r\nDhara, an\r\nedible oil brand from Mother Dairy, has rolled out a digital film on the\r\noccasion of World Heart Day 2021, advocating the importance of heart health,\r\nespecially among young Indians under the age of 40 years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The\r\ndigital film highlights the fact that todayâ€™s adults, especially under the age\r\nof 40 years, are vulnerable to cardiovascular diseases owing to the varied\r\ninconsistencies settling in modern day lifestyles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The\r\ndigital film by Dhara edible oils takes the leap from its latest brand proposition\r\nof â€˜Zara Sa Badlaavâ€™, with the essence of bringing a healthy positive change in\r\noneâ€™s daily routine. The film subtly points out the urgent need for physical\r\nexercise, reduced stress and enhancing the intake of oryzanol in daily diet as\r\nkey to heart health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The film\r\nalso shares an alarming message that 25% of heart attacks in Indian men occur\r\nunder 40*, which needs more awareness among masses. Dharaâ€™s digital film\r\nfeatures actor Shishir Sharma, who was also featured in Dharaâ€™s popular \'Jalebi ad\'.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" >Dinesh\r\nAgrawal, Business Head, Dhara, Mother Dairy Fruit and Vegetable Pvt. Ltd., said,\r\nâ€œThe modern-day course of life has inflicted various inconsistencies in our\r\nlifestyle and the events of the past two years have unfortunately compounded\r\nit. Brand Dhara has always endeavored and supported healthy lifestyle practices\r\nsuch as usage of oil in moderation and adopting routine of physical exercise.\r\nThrough this film, we aim to spread awareness amongst our current and future\r\nnation-builders to have a healthy lifestyle with due attention to heart health.\r\nWe are really glad to associate with an artist who made the brand popular in\r\nits initial days and together, we hope that our message will reach out to the\r\ndesired audience, inspiring them to be more active to lead a healthy\r\nlifestyle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The film\r\nopens with a frame featuring an active and fit senior citizen father (Shishir\r\nSharma) landing at his regular heart clinic with his son. Usually, he has been\r\nvisiting the clinic all alone for over 20 years and is well-versed with the\r\nflow around. While the son, who has accompanied his father for the first time,\r\ntries to lend a helping hand to his father for either getting down from the\r\nvehicle or to even use a wheelchair for movement, the father mentions that he\r\nhas been visiting the clinic for years and is well aware of the routine\r\nincluding the doctorâ€™s regular advice. The frame then features the duo sitting\r\noutside the doctorâ€™s room, and then there is call from the nurse for Mr.\r\nShastri. Both father and son look at each other and his father gestures the\r\nyounger Mr. Shastri to go inside. And in a surprise to viewers, this time his\r\n32-year-old son undergoes a consultation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\" >The frame\r\nthen lays out a super mentioning â€œ25% of heart attacks in Indian men occur\r\nunder 40*â€, while the voice over stresses on having a healthy heart and advise\r\nviewers to make a shift in routine by doing exercise, reducing stress and\r\nfurther increasing the intake of oryzanol in their diets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The film\r\ntowards the end also showcases Dhara Refined Ricebran Oil, which has gamma\r\noryzanol, a natural antioxidant that improves HDL/LDL ratio and lowers bad\r\ncholesterol and supports heart health. Dhara Refined Ricebran oil comes\r\nfortified with Vitamins A&amp;D, offering a nutritious choice for overall\r\nhealth. Ricebran oil is known for its high smoke point of 232Â°C (450Â°F) and\r\nmild flavour, making it suitable for high-temperature cooking methods such as\r\nstir frying and deep frying.<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Vineet\r\nKindra, Sr. Vice-President and Business Partner, DDB Mudra North, said,\r\nâ€œContrary to general perception, people under 40 are extremely vulnerable to\r\nheart diseases. We felt that World Heart Day is the right occasion for the\r\nbrand to ask people to carry out small changes in their lifestyle and oil usage\r\nfor better heart health. With â€˜Zara Sa Badlaavâ€™ people can work towards a\r\nhealthy heart.</p>', 'Marketing-Campaign', '', '#dhara#young', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-07 23:36:00', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(39, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Wonder\r\nCementâ€™s campaign showcases the spirit of new beginnings</h1>', 'wonder.jpg', 'wonder.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Cement brand Wonder Cement has launched a new\r\nTVC titled â€œJab Dil Mein Ho Jazbaat, Toh Hoti Hai #EkPerfectShuruaatâ€. Shot at\r\nthe exotic location of Pahalgam in Kashmir, the ad shares a story of a\r\ngranddaughter who is pained to see her grandmotherâ€™s house get washed away by a\r\nnatural calamity and how she strives to rebuild not only a single house&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">Cement\r\nbrand Wonder Cement has launched a new TVC titled â€œJab Dil Mein Ho Jazbaat, Toh\r\nHoti Hai #EkPerfectShuruaatâ€. Shot at the exotic location of Pahalgam in\r\nKashmir, the ad shares a story of a granddaughter who is pained to see her\r\ngrandmotherâ€™s house get washed away by a natural calamity and how she strives\r\nto rebuild not only a single house but the entire settlement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Relieved\r\nto see her grandmother safe and sound, the granddaughter invites support from\r\nher circle of friends to come contribute towards building the houses (using\r\nwonder cement) and bringing back smiles on the faces of all those who got\r\nimpacted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Vivek\r\nPatni, Director, Wonder Cement, said, â€œWe are on the trajectory of doing bigger\r\nand better things at the company and for our customers. Block by block we are\r\ngetting closer to the grand vision that we have set for ourselves and this TVC\r\nis nothing but a step towards celebrating the same. The location, the\r\nproduction team, the story and the message are all at par with the grandeur\r\nthat we want to achieve. We are aiming towards nothing short of perfection in\r\nthis and the future attempts to come.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">â€œJab Dil\r\nMein Ho Jazbaat, Toh Hoti Hai #EkPerfectShuruaat â€“ this line being so strong\r\nand powerful is really sharing the Wonder Cement spirit. We are delighted with\r\nthe TVC and are confident it will strike a chord with the customer. The ad showcases\r\nall emotions of restarting again â€“ of making a perfect shuruaat,â€ said Kiran\r\nPatil, Managing Director, Wonder Cement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class=\"text-justify\">Tarun\r\nSingh Chauhan, Brand Mentor of Wonder Cement, said, â€œ#EkPerfectShuruaat has\r\nalways been about a start. A cement bag is the beginning of a life journey of\r\nbuilding oneâ€™s own home. Wonder cement celebrates that moment. And we will\r\ncontinue to do so as we go along. We wanted to bring this out again in our TVC\r\nand have achieved it with this one. Who better than the blockbuster director of\r\nBollywood Kabir Khan to help materialise this vision. Life is unpredictable and\r\ndifficulties can strike us anytime. However, itâ€™s not what has happened that\r\nmatters, but how we bounce back from it. This TVC brings exactly this out. We\r\ncan rebuild, rejuvenate if we just have the will â€“ if we just have the\r\nJazbaat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The film\r\nis directed by Kabir Khan and scripted by Subramani Ramachandran (Subbu) from\r\nBombay Vision and on ground execution by Sadanand Parulekar from FSIV.</p>', 'Marketing-Campaign', '', '#wondercement#cement', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-07 23:51:13', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(40, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Garmin\r\nIndia launches new campaign to promote the Spirit of Outdoor Travelling<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', 'Outdoor Travelling (1).png', 'Outdoor Travelling (1).png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:PMingLiU;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">In a unique initiative, Garmin India, a unit of\r\nGarmin Ltd. (NASDAQ: GRMN), is delighted to announce the launch of an ultimate <b>Virtual\r\nTravel Platform</b> with the digital campaign â€˜<b>Open the Door to the Worldâ€™,</b>\r\nwith the aim to promote the spirit of outdoor travelling and connect travel\r\nenthusiasts to create more memorable experiences of travelling&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Introduces\r\nonline travel platform â€˜Open the Door to the Worldâ€™ to connect travelers across\r\nthe country <o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">In a unique initiative,\r\nGarmin India, a unit of Garmin Ltd. (NASDAQ: GRMN), is delighted to announce\r\nthe launch of an ultimate <b>Virtual Travel Platform</b> with the digital\r\ncampaign â€˜<b>Open the Door to the Worldâ€™,</b> with the aim to promote the\r\nspirit of outdoor travelling and connect travel enthusiasts to create more\r\nmemorable experiences of travelling across the country.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">This initiative comes\r\nagainst the backdrop of COVID-19 pandemic, which had largely restricted\r\nmobility due to the enforcement of necessary, but overwhelming, curbs across\r\nthe nation, which significantly aggravated the travel genes of people. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Through this website, Garmin\r\nintends to connect travel enthusiasts virtually to explore and fulfil their travel\r\naspirations. People who are unable to travel currently can visit the Online\r\nVirtual Travel website. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">The platform features major\r\ntravel destinations from across the globe with 360 degree imagery. With\r\nGarminâ€™s technology taking the lead role, the user can generate their virtual\r\nphoto by choosing a door and then select the destination from the 3D Map. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">The website would\r\nautomatically assist in removing the background of the initial picture and\r\nwould create a virtual travel image of the user which can be further\r\ndownloaded. Committed to provide more immersive and exciting travel\r\nexperiences, the virtual site would satisfy the urge of the travelling felt by\r\nhundreds of people.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Speaking on the initiative,</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#0E101A\"> Mr. Ali Rizvi, Director, Garmin India,</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;said</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">,</span><i><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\">â€œIn the current market scenario,\r\nwhere COVID-19 has largely restricted traveling, Garmin India has actively brought\r\nup this unique initiative to provide memorable travel experiences to our\r\ncustomers. To bring positivity and the spirit of traveling, we have developed a\r\nplatform where the users can enjoy and take their pictures across beautiful\r\nlocations. We at Garmin are constantly thriving to deliver innovative services\r\nand engage our audience in bringing the best of the experiences.\"<o:p></o:p></span></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Garmin believes there is a\r\nunique door for everyone which leads to true explorations. Considering social\r\ndistancing, health and sanitization protocols due to the pandemic, Garmin with\r\ntheir Online Virtual Travel initiative aims to bring people closer to the\r\nnature and help them venture into the world of adventure and passion by opening\r\ndoors to a different travel paradigm.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Garmin India is also running\r\na contest where the participant has to complete the â€˜Open the Door to the\r\nWorldâ€™ trip and share the virtual travel photo on social media platforms like\r\nFacebook or Instagram (public post or Facebook/Instagram Stories) with the\r\ndesignated hashtag: #GarminOutdoorSpirit. The deadline of the contest is\r\nOctober 31, 2021.&nbsp; The winners of the\r\ncontest to be announced on November 4, 2021.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN\">Link of the website</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">: </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.garmin.co.in/event/2021/outdoor/\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">https://www.garmin.co.in/event/2021/outdoor/</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">The Garmin Instinct Solar is\r\nbuilt to harness the power of the sun. The device provides unprecedented\r\nbattery life and has been loaded with tactical features like the stealth mode,\r\nthe night vision mode, etc. The smartwatch is also equipped with multiple\r\nsports modes which includes running, cycling, swimming, climbing, skiing,\r\nrowing, weightlifting and yoga.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">The Garmin F</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Ä“</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">nix Solar is designed with solar charging\r\nlenses and features industry leading technology. The devise has been integrated\r\nwith power management to provide the user with advanced battery management\r\nduring the activities.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN\">About Garmin:</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"> Engineered on the inside\r\nfor life on the outside, Garmin products have revolutionized the wellness\r\nindustry. Committed to developing wearables and health measurement tools that\r\nhelp people of all activity levels lead healthier lives, Garmin believes every\r\nday is an opportunity to innovate and a chance to beat yesterday.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoCommentText\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN\">For more information</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">, please log on to www.garmin.co.in &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Follow us at <b>Instagram</b>-\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/garminindia/?hl=en\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-style:italic\">garminindia</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-style:italic\">; <b>Facebook</b>-\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GarminIN/?fref=ts\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-style:italic\">GarminIN</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-style:italic\">; <b>Twitter</b>-\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/garmin_india\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Garmin India</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> ;\r\n<b>YouTube</b>- </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfnJ8rCWRvle4FtX2KjrTKA?sub_confirmation=1\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Garmin\r\nIndia</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#outdoortravelling#', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-08 00:00:31', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(41, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Nandu\'s to launch innovative &amp;\r\neco-friendly packaging</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', 'nandu.jpg', 'nandu.jpg', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Nandu\'s,\r\nIndia\'s largest hyperlocal and omni-channel meat brand, announced an important\r\nmilestone in its endeavor to become a truly sustainable company. The company\r\nhas launched innovative eco-friendly packaging for all its home delivery\r\norders, which promises to be a game-changer&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Nandu\'s,\r\nIndia\'s largest hyperlocal and omni-channel meat brand, announced an important\r\nmilestone in its endeavor to become a truly sustainable company. The company\r\nhas launched innovative eco-friendly packaging for all its home delivery\r\norders, which promises to be a game-changer in smart, sustainable solutions\r\nthat cater to the needs of consumers and the planet.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">A\r\nzero-waste company in the making, Nandu\'s has been responsive to the steadily\r\nshifting consumer preferences from single-use plastics to more durable,\r\nenvironment-friendly packaging alternatives. As part of its new green\r\npackaging, the primary packaging (which is in direct contact with the\r\nhygienically processed meat) is made of non-plastic virgin food-grade material\r\nthat is fully recyclable. Similarly, the secondary packaging (the outer box\r\nwhich contains the primary packaging) is made of a blend of recycled and virgin\r\npaper material that is fully recyclable, ensuring both sustainability and\r\npresentability.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Plastics\r\ntake a huge toll on the environment, contaminating the oceans and piling up at\r\nlandfills. Given that much of the plastic waste accumulates in landfills is due\r\nto food packaging, eco-friendly packaging is the need of the hour. Nandu\'s aims\r\nto meet this need by shifting this to non-plastic virgin food-grade material\r\nfor all home deliveries. Being a firm believer in sustainable solutions, the\r\ncompany is also willing to bear the overhead costs of eco-friendly packaging\r\nand offer discounts to the customers who bring their containers to the stores.\r\nThis further reduces packaging material usage, thus setting a new benchmark for\r\nother companies in the business.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Commenting\r\non this initiative, Narendra Pasuparthy, chief farmer, founder, and chief\r\nexecutive officer, Nandu\'s, said, \"We have made sustainability a part of\r\nNandu\'s DNA. As an organization, we have a strong commitment to the\r\nenvironment, ensuring that we make conscious efforts to reduce our carbon\r\nfootprint. In fact, businesses can no longer be run on balance sheets; we need\r\nto be sensitive to our ecology, drive meaningful initiatives and create a more\r\nsustainable future for our children. As far as our innovative packaging is\r\nconcerned, after a lot of deliberation and researching materials powered by our\r\nconsumers\' firm trust and loyalty, we decided on the solution that is a win-win\r\nfor us and the environment. While creating this innovation, we took all\r\nmeasures to ensure that the product quality and safety is not compromised in\r\nany way. Nandu\'s goal now is to make 100% of our packaging plastic-free by\r\n2023.\"<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">The\r\nBengaluru-based brand walks the talk from focusing on animal welfare and\r\nre-engineering feed programs (to exclude antibiotics) to investing in solar\r\nenergy and smart automation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Vinay\r\nGopinath, chief operating officer, Nandu\'s, noted, \"Nandu\'s has made\r\nitself part of the solution. Last year, for instance, when the pandemic hit us,\r\nwe started \'Bring Your Own Box\' as a proactive step in collaborating with\r\ncustomers to build trust and confidence. The results were remarkable! As they\r\nsay, where there is a will, there is a way. We have been working tirelessly to\r\nfind sustainable packaging materials as a viable alternative to plastic. Today,\r\ninnovative and planet-friendly solutions are available. The challenge is for\r\nbusinesses to see the long-term value in taking the green plunge, adopting a\r\nholistic approach to lower environmental footprint, and promoting a more\r\nsustainable culture.\"<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Since\r\nits inception in 2016, Nandu\'s has been endorsing ecologically and economically\r\nsound solutions. To reduce the burden on corn and soya, the company has been\r\nworking on an initiative called Insectifii to use insect protein as an\r\nalternative natural feed. The breeding farms, for instance, are solar-powered;\r\nthey don\'t rely on fossil fuels. Similarly, Nandu\'s uses chicken litter, which,\r\nif left in the open, emits methane - a deadly greenhouse gas- to power the\r\nbiogas plant, producing electricity consumed on the facility. The chicken\r\nlitter is also further decomposed and used as organic manure, ensuring that\r\nfarmers don\'t need to use chemical fertilizers for agricultural farming.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Pavangopal\r\nA, chief marketing officer, Nandu\'s, further added, \"Nandu\'s has been at\r\nthe forefront of embracing green practices and innovating with a future focus\r\non meeting the evolving needs of conscious consumers. Packaging is a key factor\r\nfor brands to distinguish themselves in a crowded marketplace. With\r\neco-friendly packaging solutions, it\'s easier for brands to express who they\r\nare and the values they stand for. At Nandu\'s, we make fresh, healthy,\r\nhigh-quality meat and meat products accessible for all and protect the planet,\r\npeople, and communities. Planet Positive Carbon Negative is our mantra.\"<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">The\r\nomni-channel, fully integrated farm-to-fork meat brand in Karnataka, Nandu\'s\r\nincludes retail and home delivery services via the company\'s eCommerce website,\r\napp, call center orders, and popular eCommerce marketplaces.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Product-Launches', '', '#nandu#nandus', 'Yes', NULL, '388', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-08 00:18:31', NULL, 'admin', 0),
(42, '<h1 id=\"hd1\" class=\"Poppins-Bold\">Wonder\r\nCementâ€™s campaign showcases the spirit of new beginnings</h1>', 'wonder.jpg', 'wonder.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Cement brand Wonder Cement has launched a new\r\nTVC titled â€œJab Dil Mein Ho Jazbaat, Toh Hoti Hai #EkPerfectShuruaatâ€. Shot at\r\nthe exotic location of Pahalgam in Kashmir, the ad shares a story of a\r\ngranddaughter who is pained to see her grandmotherâ€™s house get washed away by a\r\nnatural calamity and how she strives&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">Cement\r\nbrand Wonder Cement has launched a new TVC titled â€œJab Dil Mein Ho Jazbaat, Toh\r\nHoti Hai #EkPerfectShuruaatâ€. Shot at the exotic location of Pahalgam in\r\nKashmir, the ad shares a story of a granddaughter who is pained to see her\r\ngrandmotherâ€™s house get washed away by a natural calamity and how she strives\r\nto rebuild not only a single house but the entire settlement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Relieved\r\nto see her grandmother safe and sound, the granddaughter invites support from\r\nher circle of friends to come contribute towards building the houses (using\r\nwonder cement) and bringing back smiles on the faces of all those who got\r\nimpacted.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Vivek\r\nPatni, Director, Wonder Cement, said, â€œWe are on the trajectory of doing bigger\r\nand better things at the company and for our customers. Block by block we are\r\ngetting closer to the grand vision that we have set for ourselves and this TVC\r\nis nothing but a step towards celebrating the same. The location, the\r\nproduction team, the story and the message are all at par with the grandeur\r\nthat we want to achieve. We are aiming towards nothing short of perfection in\r\nthis and the future attempts to come.â€</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">â€œJab Dil\r\nMein Ho Jazbaat, Toh Hoti Hai #EkPerfectShuruaat â€“ this line being so strong\r\nand powerful is really sharing the Wonder Cement spirit. We are delighted with\r\nthe TVC and are confident it will strike a chord with the customer. The ad showcases\r\nall emotions of restarting again â€“ of making a perfect shuruaat,â€ said Kiran\r\nPatil, Managing Director, Wonder Cement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Tarun\r\nSingh Chauhan, Brand Mentor of Wonder Cement, said, â€œ#EkPerfectShuruaat has\r\nalways been about a start. A cement bag is the beginning of a life journey of\r\nbuilding oneâ€™s own home. Wonder cement celebrates that moment. And we will\r\ncontinue to do so as we go along. We wanted to bring this out again in our TVC\r\nand have achieved it with this one. Who better than the blockbuster director of\r\nBollywood Kabir Khan to help materialise this vision. Life is unpredictable and\r\ndifficulties can strike us anytime. However, itâ€™s not what has happened that\r\nmatters, but how we bounce back from it. This TVC brings exactly this out. We\r\ncan rebuild, rejuvenate if we just have the will â€“ if we just have the\r\nJazbaat.â€</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">The film\r\nis directed by Kabir Khan and scripted by Subramani Ramachandran (Subbu) from\r\nBombay Vision and on ground execution by Sadanand Parulekar from FSIV.</p>', 'Inside-Edge', '', '#wondercement#cement', 'Yes', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-08 00:20:36', NULL, 'admin', 1),
