(60, 'Garmin India brings Joy with â€˜Give A Garminâ€™ campaign in this festival season', 'giB.jpg', 'giB.jpg', '<p>Inviting customers to reward themselves with good health as a New Year gift</p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">New\r\n        Delhi, 16 December, 2021: Cheering the spirit of this festival season, Garmin India, a\r\n                unit of Garmin\r\n                Ltd. (NASDAQ: GRMN), has announced their new campaign â€˜ Give A\r\n                Garminâ€™ to invite customers to rejoice and reward themselves with\r\n            vigorous health through smartwatches from Garmin as a New Year gift.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">Customers can enjoy multiple offers along with\r\n        significant discounts on selected products in this â€˜<b>End of Yearâ€™ Sale</b>\r\n        period till January 10, 2022, making their new year more special and loaded\r\n        with fitness and other health benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">Garmin\r\n        India, a tech major, delivers innovative GPS technology across diverse markets,\r\n        including aviation, marine, fitness, outdoor recreation, tracking, and mobile\r\n        aps. The smart wearables provide an array of advanced health and fitness\r\n        features like body battery energy monitoring, pulse ox meter, health snapshot\r\n        feature providing an in-depth report of the workout, stress tracking, women\r\n        health features, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">To make\r\n        the Garmin smartwatches more accessible, the company is offering amazing deals <b>up\r\n            to 20% off on selected products.</b> The offers are as follows.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>Ã˜ Garmin\r\n            Lily (Dark Bronze, Paloma, Leather)</p>\r\n\r\n    <p><b>Offer Details: </b>MRP- Rs.\r\n        25, 990, offer price- INR\r\n            3000 off- now available at <b>Rs. 22,990</b></p>\r\n\r\n    <p><b>Link of Spec Sheet</b>: <span><a\r\n                href=\"https://www.garm