(61, 'Garmin India introduces the all new TACX BOOST', 'gii.jpg', 'gii.jpg', 'An indoor trainer designed for cyclists of all levels', '  <p>The easy-to-use Tacx Boost includes several key training features:-\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\"><span>Â·<span>Magnetic brake allows cyclists to apply\r\n                resistance or lighten it to get the most of their indoor ride\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p>\r\n        <span>Â·<span>Resistance can be adjusted manually up to\r\n                1,050 watts with 10 levels\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p>\r\n        <span>Â·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n            </span></span>\r\n        Flywheel generates authentic and smooth pedal\r\n        stroke while the closed resistance unit reduces noise\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">\r\n        <span>Â·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n            </span></span>\r\n        Speed sensor provides cyclists with an\r\n        affordable way to track speed, distance and virtual power\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\"><b>New\r\n            Delhi, 3rd January, 2022</b>:&nbsp; In a\r\n        quest to make cycling experiences more immersive, <b>Garmin India, a unit of Garmin Ltd. (NASDAQ: GRMN)</b>,\r\n        today announced\r\n        the launch of the power packed indoor training devise, the <b>Garmin TACX BOOST </b>that provides a realistic\r\n        ride-feel to the\r\n        cyclists and is ideal for training the year-round.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">The Tacx\r\n        Boost indoor trainer comes with a wide range of features. It is integrated with\r\n        ten different levels of adjustable resistance&nbsp;and can deliver up to 1,050\r\n        watts via the lever attached to the handlebar. Cycling enthusiasts can apply\r\n        resistance or lighten it with the magnetic brake to maximize their indoor\r\n        riding experience.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">The\r\n        flywheel installed in the indoor training devise simulates a realistic pedal\r\n        stroke, while the closed resistance unit helps to reduce noise, which allows\r\n        cyclists to ride anywhere without being heard. The speed sensors which comes in\r\n        separately enables the cyclists to track their pace, distance and virtual power\r\n        using apps like Tacx Training, Zwift, and TrainerRoad.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">Speaking\r\n        on the launch of Tacx Boost in India, <b>Mr. Ali Rizvi, Director, Garmin India,</b>&nbsp;said,\r\n        â€œGarmin always thrives to enhance user experiences with quality and\r\n            world-class technology. The Tacx Boost is designed and developed by the\r\n            in-house R&amp;D team to cater to the needs of cyclists of all levels and\r\n            support them in enhancing their performances. It is further laden with advanced\r\n            features and multiple applications that make it the most trusted partner while\r\n            training\".\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">The set-up\r\n        of the Tacx Boost is quite simple. The cyclists only required two simple clicks\r\n        to get it started. In addition to ensuring a comfortable cycling position, the\r\n        front wheel support also serves as a handle to carry the trainer.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\"><b>Price:</b> The Tacx Boost Indoor Trainer comes with a\r\n        speed sensor and is available in a bundle version for <b>INR 29,990.</b></p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\"><b>Availability:</b> Pro bikers (Chennai), Cyclofit\r\n        (Bombay), The Bike Shop (Gurgaon), Mastermind (Bombay) and Rajesh Cycles (New\r\n        Delhi).\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p>For more information about Tacx Boost, visit:-<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a\r\n                href=\"https://www.garmin.co.in/mobile/products/intosports/tacx-boost/\">https://www.garmin.co.in/mobile/products/intosports/tacx-boost/</a></span>\r\n\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\">Engineered\r\n        on the inside for life on the outside, Garmin products have revolutionized life\r\n        for runners, cyclists, swimmers and athletes of all levels and abilities.\r\n        Committed to developing technology that helps people stay active and elevate\r\n        performance, Garmin believes every day is an opportunity to innovate and a\r\n        chance to beat yesterday.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"text-justify\"><b><span>About Garmin International, Inc.</span></b><span> Garmin International, Inc. is a subsidiary of\r\n            Garmin Ltd. (Nasdaq: GRMN). Garmin Ltd. is incorporated in Switzerland, and its\r\n            principal subsidiaries are located in the United States, Taiwan and the United\r\n            Kingdom. Garmin is a registered trademark and Index S2 and Garmin Connect are\r\n            trademarks of Garmin Ltd. or its subsidiaries. </span></p>', 'Industry-Story', '', '#garmins #smartCycling #gadgets #cycling', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2022-01-28 05:04:44', '2022-01-28 06:47:13', 'admin', 0),
(62, 'Mondelez India\r\nlaunches OREO Double Stuf with more crÃ¨me & more play', 'Double Stuff Oreo.jpg', 'Double Stuff Oreo.jpg', 'OREO, the world\'s favourite cookie brand, today launched its globally-loved variant â€˜OREO Double Stufâ€™ in India.', ' <p class=\"text-justify\">OREO, the world\'s favourite cookie brand, today launched its\r\n        globally-loved variant â€˜OREO Double Stufâ€™ in India. Promising double the fun\r\n        and decadence with more crÃ¨me between the two scrumptious layers of its classic\r\n        cookie, this latest innovation brings to its consumers a new indulgent eat\r\n        experience. Since the brandâ€™s launch in 2011, OREO has always ushered\r\n        irresistible innovations that have enhanced snacking experience and gone beyond\r\n        being â€˜milkâ€™s favourite cookieâ€™ to one loved by all. Through its globally doted\r\n        ritual, the crunchy cookie has consistently induced playful moments in the\r\n        lives of its consumers, and with the latest launch the brand aims to deepen the\r\n        consumer love while strengthening its play in the premium biscuits category.</p>\r\n\r\n        <p  class=\"text-justify\">Commenting on the launch of the campaign,Â <b>Sunainika\r\n        Singh, head- Biscuits</b>,Â <b>Marketing, Mondelez India</b>Â says,\r\n        â€œEver since OREO made its much-awaited debut in the country a decade ago, the\r\n        brand has grown to become Indiaâ€™s much-loved cookie. Over the years, consumers\r\n        have experienced the versatility of OREO through never-seen-before eat\r\n        experiences. Be it in the form of chocolates or ice creams, or even the\r\n        unconventional recipes curated in the homes of our consumers, OREO has\r\n        successfully satiated the evolving need for new snacking experiences and\r\n        moments. The launch of â€˜OREO Double Stufâ€™ only takes this promise further and\r\n        adds to our ritual that bonds people together in acts of playfulness. A playful\r\n        mouthful, Double Stuf has been well received by cream lovers across the globe\r\n        and we are confident that it will resonate powerfully with Indian consumers as\r\n        well.â€</p>\r\n\r\n        <p class=\"text-justify\">Through an interactive and engaging 360-degree campaign, OREO\r\n        Double Stufâ€™s Twist Lick Lickâ€¦Dunk is set to create a mark for itself among\r\n        cream lovers. The brand aims to create buzz and drive engagement across social\r\n        media platforms to communicate the new productâ€™s indulgent experience to\r\n        consumers, including on Instagram and Facebook, through exciting digital\r\n        activations such as - filters to introduce their classic, globally cheered\r\n        â€œLick raceâ€ challenge. Presently, the campaign kicked off in Tamil Nadu in a\r\n        special way with Pongal celebrations.</p>\r\n\r\n        <p class=\"text-justify\">Priced at Rs 20 for 75gms and Rs.40 for 150gms, â€˜OREO Double\r\n        Stufâ€™ will be available across all trade channels.</p>', 'Industry-Story', '', '#oreo #health #healthysnack', 'No', NULL, '387', NULL, NULL, '2022-01-29 00:18:10', '2022-01-30 23:27:57', 'admin', 0),
(63, '<p>Cornitos\r\nlaunches \'Crusties\' - A 100% baked snack for the season</p>', 'Cornitos Crusties.jpg', 'Cornitos Crusties.jpg', '<p>Cornitos, the Made in India Nachos brand expands its product portfolio with baked snacks.</p>', '<p class=\"text-justify\">Cornitos, the Made in India Nachos brand expands its product\r\nportfolio with baked snacks. The newly launched range is the snack of the\r\nseason - Crusties. The funky zig-zag snack is a perfect balance of health and\r\ntaste, offering the choice to enjoy the snacks guilt-free.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">On the launch of Crusties,&nbsp;<b>Shobhit Agarwal, director,\r\nCornitos&nbsp;</b>and the mind behind the new product, said, â€œWe are excited to\r\nbring this category to our consumers, as we understand the importance of health\r\nin today time. The baked snack Crusties can be enjoyed by everyone, that\r\nincludes the millennials and GenZ who can go out and relish the snack without\r\nany guilt. Crusties is a nutrient-rich snack baked with the latest technology\r\nand uniquely flavoured. We hope to receive the same love from our customers as\r\nthey have been offering to our other products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">This range is packed with delicious flavors and incredibly\r\nnutritious ingredients such as rajma, chana, and potatoes. It is available in\r\nsix variants of Rajma Crusties King Curry, Rajma Crusties Lemon Chili, Chana\r\nCrusties Dilli Chaat, Chana Crusties Cheesy Garlic, Potato Crusties Peri Peri,\r\nand Potato Crusties Italian Cheese.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Each pack is priced at Rs 30 and would be available in retail, eTail,\r\nand modern trade stores.</p>', 'Industry-Story', '', '', 'No', NULL, '405', NULL, NULL, '2022-01-29 02:31:36', '2022-01-29 02:32:41', 'admin', 0);

